reviewText: I use the Brain Game series by National Geographic in a group at work and they love participating in the interactive parts
Purchased for my AP Psychology class.
Always interesting. Good to have around when you have visitors & there is nothing on TV you care to watch.
Boring and title is not indicative of content
Seemed geared toward a young, less-educated audience.  Not engaging for our family members (all adults).
Interesting stuff. You can't fix stupid but you can learn why people are stupid.
